Welcome to the Webmaker Activity Template!

Use this template to create activities and resources for your goals. Use a new template for each activity. Haven't thought about your goals? Try this template: 

This page requires a unique blend of HTML agility, CSS wizardry and mental firepower. There are people who are on the web, and then there are people who MAKE the web. Your goal in this project is to MAKE your very own Webmaker activity page. Add images, links and content to this page to create your very own activity page and help others teach the web.
